    "body": "Well IMO the first response here should be **you shouldn't**.  Allowing a remote page to require a local module is like giving a stranger the keys to your kingdom...  You probably shouldn't do it....\n\nWarnings aside, you can request the URL on the server either inside a BrowserWindow or inside a WebView and have `nodeIntergration` enabled for the `require` method to be available globally.\n"
